name: William R. Seward, Trustee, etc., et al., Respondents, v. Burrall Spencer et al., Trustees, etc., Impleaded, etc., Appellants

parties: William R. Seward, Trustee, etc., et al., Respondents, v. Burrall Spencer et al., Trustees, etc., Impleaded, etc., Appellants.

opinions.text:
Agree to reverse judgments of General and Special Terms. Judgment ordered for defendants, dismissing the complaint on opinion in Seward v. Huntington (ante, p. 104).
All concur.
Judgment accordingly.

casebody.head_matter:
William R. Seward, Trustee, etc., et al., Respondents, v. Burrall Spencer et al., Trustees, etc., Impleaded, etc., Appellants.
(Submitted December 3, 1883 ;
decided December 11, 1883.)
O. O. Cottle for appellants.
J. B. Perkins for respondents.
